subsection.def:
“application” (申請), in relation to the registration of
                                                  any matter, means an application in the specified
                                                  form;

“appointed day” (指定日期) means the day
                                                  appointed under section 1(2) for the
                                                  commencement of section 21;

“chargor” (押記人) means the owner of registered land,
                                                  or the lessee of a registered long term lease,
                                                  which is subject to a charge;

“entry” (記項), in relation to the Title Register,
                                                  means a note, notice or other entry in the Title
                                                  Register; and “enter” and “entered” (記入) shall be construed accordingly;

“image record” (影像紀錄) means a record produced using the
                                                  imaging method and, where the context permits,
                                                  includes a record in a legible form;

